# m6_damage_number_bold_compare.shot — side-by-side weight comparison
#
# Drives one damage event of each tier from a stationary mech so that
# all five glyphs share a frame at roughly the same height. Used to
# eyeball the per-tier outline + fake-bold weight progression.

window 1280 720
seed 1 1
out build/shots/m6_damage_number_bold_compare
map slipstream
no_parallax
loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" Sidearm Light Standard

spawn_at 1500 1176
mouse 1180 360

extra_chassis Heavy 1700 1176

at 30 shot pre_damage

# Stagger 1 tick apart so all five glyphs hang together near spawn,
# tier order left→right LIGHT → CRIT.
at 35 damage 2 CHEST 5      # LIGHT
at 36 damage 2 CHEST 20     # NORMAL
at 37 damage 2 CHEST 45     # MEDIUM
at 38 damage 2 CHEST 75     # HEAVY
at 39 damage 2 CHEST 150    # CRIT

at 42 shot t000_all_airborne
at 50 shot t008_just_after
at 75 shot t033_midflight

contact_sheet bold_compare cols 4 cell 480 270

at 120 end
